---
Source:
  Page: 164
  Title: The Pocket Buddha Reader
Title: Majjhima Nikaya
---
Let the past be and forget the future.
Learn that which is now.

When this condition is, that condition comes to be.
With the arising of this, that arises.
When this is not here, that does not come into existence.
With the ceasing of this, that ceases also.
